(I have a bad feeling about what's ahead... I can't go on
with my stomach like this...)

\AA[FFFF]\FFFF[1014Furea_0005]\N<Pure Flame>Everyone, over here!! I will now undo the BB Gang's
brainwashing!! Please line up!!

\FFFF[1014Furea_0005]\N<Citizen>Please, do something...!! My, my head... feels like it's
going to burst...!!

\AA[FFFF]\FFFF[1014Furea_0014]\N<Pure Flame>Yes, it's alright, it's alright. That discomfort will soon
disappear... hehehe.
\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0005]\FFFF[1014Furea_0003]\N<Pure Flame>I am Pure Flame!! Who are you, reveal your true identity!!

\FX[F]\AA[FFFF]\F[1012Furea_0005]\FFFF[1014Furea_0012]\N<Pure Flame>I am the real Pure Flame!! Everyone, do not be deceived!!
That one must be a fake sent by the BB Gang!!
\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0017]\FFFF[1014Furea_0012]\N<Pure Flame>What!? The fake one is you!? Stop talking nonsense!!

\FX[F]\F[1012Furea_0017]\FFFF[1014Furea_0012]\N<Citizen>Which... which one is the real one...!? Who's telling the
truth...!?

\FX[F]\AA[FFFF]\F[1012Furea_0012]\FFFF[1014Furea_0018]\N<Pure Flame>It can't be helped now!! I will have to resort to force!!
Pure Flame, here I come!!

\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0017]\FFFF[1014Furea_0018]\N<Pure Flame>That's my line!! I'll show you that the real one cannot lose
to a fake!! Pure Flame, here I come!!

\FX[F]\AA[FFFF]\F[1012Furea_0013]\FFFF[1014Furea_0012]\N<Pure Flame>You've shamelessly come again, impostor!! No matter how many
times you come, the result will be the same!!
\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0013]\FFFF[4050Robot]\N<Pure Flame>Haa haa haa... Somehow... we won!!
\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0013]\FFFF[4050Robot]\N<Pure Flame>I can't believe... that robot was disguised as me...

\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0003]\FFFF[4050Robot]\N<Pure Flame>!! That's right, we need to destroy the brainwashing device
quickly!!
\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0005]\N<Pure Flame>Phew, that takes care of that...!!
\FX[F]\AA[FFFFF]\F[1012Furea_0005]\FFFFF[9020OtokoA]\N<Citizen>It, it's gone!! My headache is gone!!
\FX[F]\FX[FFF]\AA[FFF]\F[9021OtokoB]\FFF[1012Furea_0004]\N<Pure Flame>I'm glad, now we can safely return to the base...
\FX[F]\FX[FFF]\AA[F]\M[jumpjump]\F[9021OtokoB]\FFF[1012Furea_0003]\N<Citizen>Wow, the real Pure Flame. Gotta take a photo!!
\FX[FFF]\AA[FFFFF]\MMMMM[no]\FFF[1012Furea_0003]\FFFFF[9021OtokoB]\N<Citizen>Ohhoo~, that ass line, so lewd...♡ Are you tempting me♡

\FX[F]\AA[FFF]\F[9021OtokoB]\FFF[1012Furea_0012]\N<Pure Flame>Why you ask... I am not doing this as a spectacle or
cosplay...!!

emphasizes your cleavage a bit more?

prepared...

\FX[F]\AA[FFFFF]\F[1012Furea_0012]\FFFFF[2030DarkSoldier_0000]\N<Dark Soldier>I've been waiting for you, Pure Flame.
\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0005]\FFFFF[2030DarkSoldier_0000]\N<Pure Flame>Been waiting...? It's as if you knew I would come here!!

\FX[F]\AA[FFFFF]\F[1012Furea_0005]\FFFFF[2030DarkSoldier_0000]\N<Dark Soldier>Yes, I knew. I've been watching you since the first time you
transformed... And at that moment, I instinctively thought.
\FX[F]\AA[FFFFF]\F[1012Furea_0005]\FFFFF[2030DarkSoldier_0000]\N<Dark Soldier>"This one could stand against me"...

\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0005]\FFFFF[2030DarkSoldier_0000]\N<Pure Flame>...I'm honored you think so highly of my power. But if
that's the case, why did you leave me, a dangerous element
to the BB gang, unchecked? There should be no benefit for
you in allowing me to grow stronger...

\FX[F]\AA[FFFFF]\F[1012Furea_0005]\FFFFF[2030DarkSoldier_0000]\N<Dark Soldier>Huhuhu... A natural question... But the answer is quite
simple.

\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0009]\FFFFF[2030DarkSoldier_0000]\N<Pure Flame>I understand. Then let me show you my growth and power...!!
And please, release those who have been brainwashed!!

brainwashing device. Destroying it will end the battle.

\FX[F]\AA[FFFFF]\F[1012Furea_0009]\FFFFF[2030DarkSoldier_0000]\N<Dark Soldier>...If you can defeat me safely, that is!! Let's go, Pure
